.TH KANBANANA 1 "February 2026" "kanbanana 0.1.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
kanbanana \- a kanban CLI foundation for coding agents
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B kanbanana
.RI [ --json ]
.RI [ --help ]
.RI [ --version ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B kanbanana
prints a minimal starter board for agent-focused kanban workflows.

By default, output is plain text.
Use
.B --json
for machine-readable output.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B --help, -h
Show help text and exit.
.TP
.B --version, -v
Show version and exit.
.TP
.B --json
Print the starter board as JSON.
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
Show help:
.B kanbanana --help
.TP
Print JSON output:
.B kanbanana --json
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Successful execution.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR npm (1)
